# Prodige Workflow Pointer

Read and follow `AGENTS.md` before taking action. Then load `.ai/boot/BOOT.md`,
`.ai/SOUL.md`, `.ai/orchestrator/ORCHESTRATOR.md`, and `.ai/skills/manifest.json`.

Route `/command` messages through `.ai/commands/registry.json`. Use the Prodige
MCP server (`node .ai/scripts/prodige-mcp.js`) when available for context,
locks, gates, and next-action suggestions.
